race.comment: OUTLAW ANNIE (5) gave a bold sight as favourite when resuming at Gilgandra but was collared late to finish second. Is sure to have come on from that and has enough pace to offset the wide draw. Expect her to charge forward again and prove tougher to reel in. NIGHTWALKER (9) is knocking on the door, placing in all four runs back this campaign. Backs up quickly and doesn't have to improve much to get the job done. MEDIA SPIN (1) is a Press Statement gelding on debut for the Lundholm stable. Found the line nicely in his recent trial when beaten a head. Gets a key booking in Gallagher and can make an immediate impact. FRENCH HARP (8) returns and deserves consideration. Watch for late money.
